_sText:
A little fun map for everyone

map info:
Cubemap
Skybox
Spinning objects
Traps
music
teleport
and so on 

weapons:
knife
flashbang
he grenade

the idea of map is of course t's vs ct's 
all of the circles in the middle of the map spins with makes a fun fast paced gameplay

some pretty awesome soundtracks can be enabled by clicking buttons in each side out on the platform with stairs

there is 3 traps throughout the level wich will reveal themself at a specific point in the map time

Enjoy
